# Production build config (loaded by Vite for `vite build`).
# The front is served as a static bundle (`serve -s dist`, no /api proxy), so the
# API base URL must be an absolute origin — the paired custom domain of keepou-api.
# Vite inlines this AT BUILD TIME: change it here → rebuild keepou-web to take effect.
# A Railway service variable named VITE_API_URL, if set, overrides this file.
VITE_API_URL=https://api-keepou.galaxou.com
